
## Anti-Patterns (Forbidden)

- ❌ `console.log()` — use Logger or toast notifications
- ❌ `: any` — use proper TypeScript types
- ❌ Hard-coded secrets — use environment variables
- ❌ `process.env` directly in business code — use a config service

